<div class="container content">
	<div class="row margin-bottom-30">
		<div class="col-md-7 mb-margin-bottom-30">
			<div class="headline"><h2>강의 평가 작성하기</h2></div>
			<p>우측(데스크탑) 또는 하단(모바일)에 있는 규칙들을 충분히 숙지하시고 작성해주세요.</p>

			<br />
      <%= bootstrap_form_for [@lecture_info, @lecture_estimate], html: {multipart: true, id: "sky-form3", class: "sky-form sky-changes-3 contact-style", novalidate: "novalidate"} do |f| %>
        <% if @lecture_estimate.errors.any? %>
          <div id="error_explanation">
            <h2><%= pluralize(@post.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this post from being saved:</h2>

            <ul>
            <% @lecture_estimate.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
              <li><%= message %></li>
            <% end %>
            </ul>
          </div>
        <% end %>
					<div class='row'>
						<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 text-center">
              <%= f.select(:reason, options_for_select([['학점', '학점'], ['흥미', '흥미'],['배움', '배움']]), label: "수강 이유" ) %>
						</div>
					</div>
					<br />
					<div class='row'>
						<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
							<div class="br-theme-fontawesome-stars" >
	              <%= f.select(:fun, options_for_select([['1', 20], ['2', 40],['3', 60],['4', 80],['5', 100]]),{label: "흥미 & 재미"}, class: "star-rating" ) %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
							<div class="br-theme-fontawesome-stars" >
              	<%= f.select(:teaching, options_for_select([['1', 20], ['2', 40],['3', 60],['4', 80],['5', 100]]),{label: "교수력"}, class: "star-rating" ) %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
							<div class="br-theme-fontawesome-stars" >
		            <%= f.select(:get_grade, options_for_select([['1', 20], ['2', 40],['3', 60],['4', 80],['5', 100]]),{label: "학점따기"}, class: "star-rating" ) %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-3 text-center">
							<div class="br-theme-fontawesome-stars">
              	<%= f.select(:teamwork_n_asg, options_for_select([['1', 20], ['2', 40],['3', 60],['4', 80],['5', 100]]),{label: "과제 & 조모임"}, class: "star-rating" ) %>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class='row'>
            <%= f.text_area :msg, class: "summernote", id: "summernote-post", label: "후기" %>
					</div>
				</fieldset>

				<footer class='text-center'>
          <%= f.submit "작성하기", class: "btn-u btn-u-lg" %>
				</footer>

				<div class="message">
					<i class="rounded-x fa fa-check"></i>
					<p>Your message was successfully sent!</p>
				</div>
			<% end %>
		</div><!--/col-md-9-->

		<div class="col-md-5">
			<div class="headline"><h2>커뮤니티 매너</h2></div>
			<p>아래의 기본적인 예의를 지켜주세요.</p>
			<ul class="list-unstyled margin-bottom-30">
				<li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i> <strong>예의</strong>를 지켜주세요.</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i> 상대를 <strong>존중</strong>해주세요.</li>
				<li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i> 타인을 지칭할 때 <strong>***님</strong>으로 불러주세요.</li>
			</ul>

		</div><!--/col-md-3-->
	</div><!--/row-->
</div>
